-- Three-Month Copper Futures Climb by 1.1% in London, Advance for Fifth Day
-- Glenys Sim
-- 2010-06-14T00:02:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/three-month-copper-futures-climb-by-1-1-in-london-advance-for-fifth-day.html

          
          
             Three-month copper futures on the
London Metal Exchange gained for a fifth day, rising as much as
1.1 percent to $6,550 a metric ton. Aluminum futures also
advanced.  
